OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781939880
OL,3,CTrain crash passenger saw 'bloodied
OL,4,Cfaces' and people 'in a very bad way'
OL,6,FHe said: "I got up and I saw seats
OL,7,Feverywhere, there were people on my
OL,8,Flap.
OL,10,F"There was people in the aisle,
OL,11,Fpeople's faces all bloodied. I've seen
OL,12,Fthat people's legs were broken. Some
OL,13,Felderly people were unresponsive.
OL,15,FPeter Knapp was one of the first
OL,16,Fpeople off the train and recorded this
OL,17,Ffootage
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
