PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781939880
OL,3,CTrain crash passenger saw 'bloodied
OL,4,Cfaces' and people 'in a very bad way'
OL,6,F"Some people were unable to speak; it
OL,7,Flooked to me as though there were some
OL,8,Fpeople in that front carriage, maybe
OL,9,Fin a very bad way."
OL,11,FBritish Transport Police said a train
OL,12,Fdriver had been killed and several
OL,13,Fother people injured in the collision
OL,14,Fbetween the two East Midlands Railway
OL,15,Ftrains.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
