PN,31104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781939880
OL,3,CTrain crash passenger saw 'bloodied
OL,4,Cfaces' and people 'in a very bad way'
OL,6,FThe two trains involved in the
OL,7,Fcollision were the 4.40pm EMR service
OL,8,Ffrom Corby to London St Pancras and
OL,9,Fthe 3.50pm Nottingham to London St
OL,10,FPancras service. The crash happened
OL,11,Fjust south of the Elstow interchange
OL,12,Fbetween the A421 and the A6.
OL,14,FMr Knapp said he wandered across the
OL,15,Frailway track in shock before stopping
OL,16,Fin a field next to the crash site.
OL,18,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
