OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781939880
OL,3,CTrain crash passenger saw 'bloodied
OL,4,Cfaces' and people 'in a very bad way'
OL,6,FHe said: "I've got blood all over my
OL,7,Ftrousers and my back hurts like hell,
OL,8,Fbut I'm alright."
OL,10,FMr Knapp added he had not felt the
OL,11,Ftrain slow down before the crash, but
OL,12,Fother passengers told him they had.
OL,14,FBedford Hospital and Luton and
OL,15,FDunstable University Hospital have
OL,16,Fboth said they were dealing with an
OL,17,Finflux of patients and urged people to
OL,18,Fstay away from their emergency
OL,19,Fdepartments "unless they have a
OL,20,Fgenuine medical emergency."
