OL,3,CTrain crash passenger saw 'bloodied
OL,4,Cfaces' and people 'in a very bad way'
OL,6,FNumerous ambulances and air ambulances
OL,7,Fwere at the scene on Friday, with a
OL,8,Fmassive emergency service presence on
OL,9,Fhand responding to the crash.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/6
